title: Join us on a tour of the Vienna Central Cemetery
description: On the outskirts of Vienna, more than 3 million people are buried in the Vienna Central Cemetery — including  Beethoven, Strauss and one of Austria's most celebrated musicians, Falco.

itunes:author: Raina Douris
